.TH "LZR" "1" "Jan 2026" "lazyray" "lazyray Manual"

.SH NAME
lzr-update - Manage xray-core updates


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBlzr update [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage the pinned xray-core engine that lazyray runs as its proxy core. Use 'lzr update check' to compare the installed xray-core against the pinned release, and 'lzr update apply' to download and install it.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for update


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBlzr(1)\fP, \fBlzr-update-apply(1)\fP, \fBlzr-update-check(1)\fP
